title: LOL Analysis and Prediction Model.
description: League of Legends Vision Control and Support Role Analysis is a comprehensive data science project including in-depth analysis, starting from EDA to hypothesis testing, development of baseline models, and a fairness analysis of game dynamics and player roles in League of Legends.

title: N-Gram Language Model
description: Created N-Gram-based language model to analyze and generate text sequences. Implemented tokenization and generation for unigram, bigram, and higher-order models. Trained probabilistic models by computing conditional probabilities of tokens.

title: Public Transportation Optimizer
description: Developed a data-driven solution to analyze and optimize bus schedules, simulate passenger experiences, and visualize key insights to enhance transportation efficiency. Wrote algorithms to calculate shortest paths and assess scheduling performance.

title: TicTrac Study Tracker
description: Designed and created a sophisticated web application with Next.js and React.js to monitor time elapsed on tasks for multiple users, featuring seamless backend integration with Firebase for real-time data handling and dynamic user interfaces.

title: Spotify Song Searcher
description: Made a program using a recommendation algorithm to search for songs based on keywords and lyrics recommend songs in a given database based on song attributes such as valence, energy, key, loudness, and tempo
